             sworn.</p>
               <p>(Produces the property); I received this from Mr. Cook, and have had it ever since.</p>
               <p>Cook. This is the exact piece that the prisoner took out of my shop.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I have not any thing to say in my defence, I leave it to the mercy of the Court.(The prisoner called two witnesses, who gave him a good character).</p>
               <p>
